1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:13,200
This is tough. Our business suffered a serious blow here.

2
00:00:13,280 --> 00:00:15,280
The truth is, we still have not processed it.

3
00:00:16,039 --> 00:00:19,240
This is an event on a scale that is hard for us to even comprehend.

4
00:00:19,800 --> 00:00:23,080
We invested our essence here, everything we could.

5
00:00:24,080 --> 00:00:27,199
We put a lot of love into this. Every board that came out of here was love.

6
00:00:27,199 --> 00:00:30,119
We did this out of values of Hebrew labor,

7
00:00:30,719 --> 00:00:33,320
of the Land of Israel, of the people of Israel.

8
00:00:33,399 --> 00:00:36,320
Our whole lives are here, truly. This is our baby

9
00:00:36,399 --> 00:00:39,000
and our lives are truly here.

10
00:00:41,799 --> 00:00:46,560
All the goods behind me that were left are orders for farms, for hilltop communities...

11
00:00:46,640 --> 00:00:51,399
Everything is made with Hebrew labor, with love for the craft and with manual work.

12
00:00:51,480 --> 00:00:54,920
We really feel a small taste of the destruction of the Temple.

13
00:00:54,920 --> 00:00:58,120
We will rise up, we will succeed, and we will grow stronger,

14
00:00:58,200 --> 00:01:00,920
and we will continue to hold on to the Land of Israel.

15
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:05,799
And we believe that we will come out of this stronger and greater.

16
00:01:05,920 --> 00:01:09,640
Only the people of Israel are the support that gives us strength. Thank you.

17
00:01:09,719 --> 00:01:13,799
Thank you very much to the entire people of Israel, for the partnership and for this warm embrace,

18
00:01:13,879 --> 00:01:16,120
it truly warms the heart.
